### ‚úÖ 1. Sync Project Tech Stack (Recommended)
# This clears old techs and sets the new list.
# Best for "Edit Project" forms with checkboxes.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/project-tech/{{projectId}}/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technologyIds": ["{{techId1}}", "{{techId2}}"]
}


### ‚úÖ 2. Add Tech to Existing Stack
# Appends new technologies without removing current ones.
POST {{baseUrl}}/project-tech/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technologyIds": ["{{techId1}}"]
}


### üîç 3. Get Project's Tech Stack
# Returns the list of technologies linked to this project.
GET {{baseUrl}}/project-tech/{{projectId}}


### üóëÔ∏è 4. Remove Specific Tech from Project
# Unlinks only ONE technology from the project.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project-tech/{{projectId}}/{{techId1}}